{
  "name": "create_complete_dashboard",
  "description": "Create a dashboard with layout, tab, and widgets.\n\nIMPORTANT: Before creating GRAPH widgets, you MUST use list_object_metadata_items to get valid objectMetadataId and field IDs.\n\nGRID SYSTEM:\n- 12 columns (0-11), rows start at 0\n- Full width: columnSpan: 12, Half: columnSpan: 6, Third: columnSpan: 4\n- Row spans: 2-4 (KPI), 6-8 (charts)\n\nWIDGET TYPES:\n\n1. GRAPH with configurationType \"AGGREGATE_CHART\" (KPI number):\n   - Requires: objectMetadataId, configuration.configurationType, configuration.aggregateFieldMetadataId, configuration.aggregateOperation\n   - Example: { type: \"GRAPH\", objectMetadataId: \"<opportunity-object-uuid>\", configuration: { configurationType: \"AGGREGATE_CHART\", aggregateFieldMetadataId: \"<amount-field-uuid>\", aggregateOperation: \"SUM\" } }\n\n2. GRAPH with configurationType \"BAR_CHART\":\n   - Additional required: configuration.primaryAxisGroupByFieldMetadataId, configuration.layout (\"VERTICAL\" or \"HORIZONTAL\")\n   - IMPORTANT: When grouping by a RELATION field (e.g. owner, company), you MUST provide primaryAxisGroupBySubFieldName (e.g. \"name\", \"email\") \u2014 otherwise it groups by raw UUID which is useless. Composite fields (e.g. address) also require a subfield (e.g. \"addressCity\").\n   - Example (simple field): { type: \"GRAPH\", objectMetadataId: \"<opportunity-object-uuid>\", configuration: { configurationType: \"BAR_CHART\", aggregateFieldMetadataId: \"<amount-field-uuid>\", aggregateOperation: \"COUNT\", primaryAxisGroupByFieldMetadataId: \"<stage-field-uuid>\", layout: \"VERTICAL\" } }\n   - Example (relation field): { type: \"GRAPH\", objectMetadataId: \"<opportunity-object-uuid>\", configuration: { configurationType: \"BAR_CHART\", aggregateFieldMetadataId: \"<amount-field-uuid>\", aggregateOperation: \"SUM\", primaryAxisGroupByFieldMetadataId: \"<company-field-uuid>\", primaryAxisGroupBySubFieldName: \"name\", layout: \"VERTICAL\" } }\n\n3. GRAPH with configurationType \"LINE_CHART\":\n   - Additional required: configuration.primaryAxisGroupByFieldMetadataId\n   - Example: { type: \"GRAPH\", objectMetadataId: \"<opportunity-object-uuid>\", configuration: { configurationType: \"LINE_CHART\", aggregateFieldMetadataId: \"<amount-field-uuid>\", aggregateOperation: \"SUM\", primaryAxisGroupByFieldMetadataId: \"<created-date-field-uuid>\" } }\n\n4. GRAPH with configurationType \"PIE_CHART\":\n   - Additional required: configuration.groupByFieldMetadataId (note: different field name!)\n   - Example: { type: \"GRAPH\", objectMetadataId: \"<opportunity-object-uuid>\", configuration: { configurationType: \"PIE_CHART\", aggregateFieldMetadataId: \"<id-field-uuid>\", aggregateOperation: \"COUNT\", groupByFieldMetadataId: \"<stage-field-uuid>\" } }\n\n5. IFRAME: { type: \"IFRAME\", configuration: { configurationType: \"IFRAME\", url: \"https://...\" } }\n\n6. STANDALONE_RICH_TEXT: { type: \"STANDALONE_RICH_TEXT\", configuration: { configurationType: \"STANDALONE_RICH_TEXT\", body: { ... } } }\n\n7. RECORD_TABLE: displays a live, filterable record list directly on the dashboard.\n   - IMPORTANT: you MUST create a dedicated view for the widget BEFORE creating the widget. Use create_view to create a new TABLE view for the object, then pass its ID as viewId. Never reuse an existing index-page view \u2014 widget views and record index views must not overlap.\n   - Requires: objectMetadataId (top-level, UUID of the object to display) AND configuration.viewId (UUID of the dedicated view you just created)\n   - configuration.configurationType must be \"RECORD_TABLE\"\n   - Recommended size: rowSpan 8-10, columnSpan 12 (full width)\n   - Workflow: (1) call create_view with type TABLE for the object \u2192 get the viewId, (2) call create_many_view_fields to add visible columns to that view, (3) create the widget with that viewId\n   - Example: { type: \"RECORD_TABLE\", objectMetadataId: \"<object-uuid>\", configuration: { configurationType: \"RECORD_TABLE\", viewId: \"<dedicated-view-uuid>\" } }\n\nAGGREGATION OPERATIONS: COUNT, SUM, AVG, MIN, MAX, COUNT_EMPTY, COUNT_NOT_EMPTY",
  "inputSchema": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "title": {
        "description": "Dashboard title",
        "type": "string"
      },
      "tabTitle": {
        "description": "Title of the first tab",
        "default": "Main",
        "type": "string"
      },
      "widgets": {
        "description": "Widgets to add",
        "default": [],
        "type": "array",
        "items": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "title": {
              "description": "Widget title displayed in the header",
              "type": "string"
            },
            "type": {
              "description": "Widget type",
              "type": "string",
              "enum": [
                "VIEW",
                "GRAPH",
                "IFRAME",
                "STANDALONE_RICH_TEXT",
                "RECORD_TABLE"
              ]
            },
            "gridPosition": {
              "description": "Position in 12-column grid",
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
                "row": {
                  "description": "Row position (0-based)",
                  "type": "number",
                  "minimum": 0
                },
                "column": {
                  "description": "Column position (0-11 for 12-column grid)",
                  "type": "number",
                  "minimum": 0,
                  "maximum": 11
                },
                "rowSpan": {
                  "description": "Number of rows the widget spans",
                  "type": "number",
                  "minimum": 1
                },
                "columnSpan": {
                  "description": "Number of columns the widget spans (1-12)",
                  "type": "number",
                  "minimum": 1,
                  "maximum": 12
                }
              },
              "required": [
                "row",
                "column",
                "rowSpan",
                "columnSpan"
              ]
            },
            "objectMetadataId": {
              "description": "REQUIRED for GRAPH and RECORD_TABLE widgets: UUID of the object to aggregate or display",
              "type": "string",
              "format": "uuid"
            },
            "configuration": {
              "description": "Widget configuration - structure depends on widget type",
              "anyOf": [
                {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "configurationType": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "const": "AGGREGATE_CHART"
                    },
                    "aggregateFieldMetadataId": {
                      "description": "Field UUID to aggregate (must be from the widget objectMetadataId)",
                      "type": "string",
                      "format": "uuid"
                    },
                    "aggregateOperation": {
                      "description": "Aggregation operation: COUNT, SUM, AVG, MIN, MAX, etc.",
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "MIN",
                        "MAX",
                        "AVG",
                        "SUM",
                        "COUNT",
                        "COUNT_UNIQUE_VALUES",
                        "COUNT_EMPTY",
                        "COUNT_NOT_EMPTY",
                        "COUNT_TRUE",
                        "COUNT_FALSE",
                        "PERCENTAGE_EMPTY",
                        "PERCENTAGE_NOT_EMPTY"
                      ]
                    },
                    "label": {
                      "type": "string"
                    },
                    "displayDataLabel": {
                      "default": true,
                      "type": "boolean"
                    },
                    "prefix": {
                      "type": "string"
                    },
                    "suffix": {
                      "type": "string"
                    },
                    "ratioAggregateConfig": {
                      "type": "object",
                      "properties": {
                        "fieldMetadataId": {
                          "type": "string",
                          "format": "uuid"
                        },
                        "optionValue": {
                          "type": "string"
                        }
                      },
                      "required": [
                        "fieldMetadataId",
                        "optionValue"
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  "required": [
                    "configurationType",
                    "aggregateFieldMetadataId",
                    "aggregateOperation",
                    "displayDataLabel"
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "configurationType": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "const": "BAR_CHART"
                    },
                    "aggregateFieldMetadataId": {
                      "description": "Field UUID to aggregate",
                      "type": "string",
                      "format": "uuid"
                    },
                    "aggregateOperation": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "MIN",
                        "MAX",
                        "AVG",
                        "SUM",
                        "COUNT",
                        "COUNT_UNIQUE_VALUES",
                        "COUNT_EMPTY",
                        "COUNT_NOT_EMPTY",
                        "COUNT_TRUE",
                        "COUNT_FALSE",
                        "PERCENTAGE_EMPTY",
                        "PERCENTAGE_NOT_EMPTY"
                      ]
                    },
                    "primaryAxisGroupByFieldMetadataId": {
                      "description": "Field UUID to group by on primary axis",
                      "type": "string",
                      "format": "uuid"
                    },
                    "primaryAxisGroupBySubFieldName": {
                      "description": "REQUIRED for relation fields (e.g. \"name\", \"address.addressCity\") and composite fields (e.g. \"addressCity\"). Without this, relation fields group by raw UUID which is not useful.",
                      "type": "string"
                    },
                    "secondaryAxisGroupByFieldMetadataId": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "format": "uuid"
                    },
                    "secondaryAxisGroupBySubFieldName": {
                      "description": "REQUIRED for relation fields (e.g. \"name\", \"stage\") and composite fields (e.g. \"addressCity\"). Without this, relation fields group by raw UUID which is not useful.",
                      "type": "string"
                    },
                    "primaryAxisOrderBy": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "FIELD_ASC",
                        "FIELD_DESC",
                        "FIELD_POSITION_ASC",
                        "FIELD_POSITION_DESC",
                        "VALUE_ASC",
                        "VALUE_DESC",
                        "MANUAL"
                      ]
                    },
                    "primaryAxisManualSortOrder": {
                      "type": "array",
                      "items": {
                        "type": "string"
                      }
                    },
                    "secondaryAxisOrderBy": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "FIELD_ASC",
                        "FIELD_DESC",
                        "FIELD_POSITION_ASC",
                        "FIELD_POSITION_DESC",
                        "VALUE_ASC",
                        "VALUE_DESC",
                        "MANUAL"
                      ]
                    },
                    "secondaryAxisManualSortOrder": {
                      "type": "array",
                      "items": {
                        "type": "string"
                      }
                    },
                    "omitNullValues": {
                      "type": "boolean"
                    },
                    "primaryAxisDateGranularity": {
                      "description": "Date grouping granularity for X axis",
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "DAY",
                        "WEEK",
                        "MONTH",
                        "QUARTER",
                        "YEAR",
                        "DAY_OF_THE_WEEK",
                        "MONTH_OF_THE_YEAR",
                        "QUARTER_OF_THE_YEAR"
                      ]
                    },
                    "secondaryAxisGroupByDateGranularity": {
                      "description": "Date grouping granularity for secondary grouping",
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "DAY",
                        "WEEK",
                        "MONTH",
                        "QUARTER",
                        "YEAR",
                        "DAY_OF_THE_WEEK",
                        "MONTH_OF_THE_YEAR",
                        "QUARTER_OF_THE_YEAR"
                      ]
                    },
                    "color": {
                      "description": "Chart color theme",
                      "$ref": "#/$defs/_f7"
                    },
                    "axisNameDisplay": {
                      "description": "Which axis labels to show",
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "NONE",
                        "X",
                        "Y",
                        "BOTH"
                      ]
                    },
                    "displayDataLabel": {
                      "default": false,
                      "type": "boolean"
                    },
                    "displayLegend": {
                      "default": true,
                      "type": "boolean"
                    },
                    "groupMode": {
                      "description": "Bar display mode when using secondary grouping",
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "STACKED",
                        "GROUPED"
                      ]
                    },
                    "isCumulative": {
                      "description": "Show running totals",
                      "type": "boolean"
                    },
                    "rangeMin": {
                      "description": "Y axis minimum value",
                      "type": "number"
                    },
                    "rangeMax": {
                      "description": "Y axis maximum value",
                      "type": "number"
                    },
                    "layout": {
                      "description": "Layout orientation for bar charts",
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "VERTICAL",
                        "HORIZONTAL"
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  "required": [
                    "configurationType",
                    "aggregateFieldMetadataId",
                    "aggregateOperation",
                    "primaryAxisGroupByFieldMetadataId",
                    "displayDataLabel",
                    "displayLegend",
                    "layout"
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "configurationType": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "const": "LINE_CHART"
                    },
                    "aggregateFieldMetadataId": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "format": "uuid"
                    },
                    "aggregateOperation": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "MIN",
                        "MAX",
                        "AVG",
                        "SUM",
                        "COUNT",
                        "COUNT_UNIQUE_VALUES",
                        "COUNT_EMPTY",
                        "COUNT_NOT_EMPTY",
                        "COUNT_TRUE",
                        "COUNT_FALSE",
                        "PERCENTAGE_EMPTY",
                        "PERCENTAGE_NOT_EMPTY"
                      ]
                    },
                    "primaryAxisGroupByFieldMetadataId": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "format": "uuid"
                    },
                    "primaryAxisGroupBySubFieldName": {
                      "description": "REQUIRED for relation fields (e.g. \"name\", \"address.addressCity\") and composite fields (e.g. \"addressCity\"). Without this, relation fields group by raw UUID which is not useful.",
                      "type": "string"
                    },
                    "secondaryAxisGroupByFieldMetadataId": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "format": "uuid"
                    },
                    "secondaryAxisGroupBySubFieldName": {
                      "description": "REQUIRED for relation fields (e.g. \"name\", \"stage\") and composite fields (e.g. \"addressCity\"). Without this, relation fields group by raw UUID which is not useful.",
                      "type": "string"
                    },
                    "primaryAxisOrderBy": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "FIELD_ASC",
                        "FIELD_DESC",
                        "FIELD_POSITION_ASC",
                        "FIELD_POSITION_DESC",
                        "VALUE_ASC",
                        "VALUE_DESC",
                        "MANUAL"
                      ]
                    },
                    "primaryAxisManualSortOrder": {
                      "type": "array",
                      "items": {
                        "type": "string"
                      }
                    },
                    "secondaryAxisOrderBy": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "FIELD_ASC",
                        "FIELD_DESC",
                        "FIELD_POSITION_ASC",
                        "FIELD_POSITION_DESC",
                        "VALUE_ASC",
                        "VALUE_DESC",
                        "MANUAL"
                      ]
                    },
                    "secondaryAxisManualSortOrder": {
                      "type": "array",
                      "items": {
                        "type": "string"
                      }
                    },
                    "omitNullValues": {
                      "type": "boolean"
                    },
                    "primaryAxisDateGranularity": {
                      "description": "Date grouping granularity for X axis",
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "DAY",
                        "WEEK",
                        "MONTH",
                        "QUARTER",
                        "YEAR",
                        "DAY_OF_THE_WEEK",
                        "MONTH_OF_THE_YEAR",
                        "QUARTER_OF_THE_YEAR"
                      ]
                    },
                    "secondaryAxisGroupByDateGranularity": {
                      "description": "Date grouping granularity for secondary grouping",
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "DAY",
                        "WEEK",
                        "MONTH",
                        "QUARTER",
                        "YEAR",
                        "DAY_OF_THE_WEEK",
                        "MONTH_OF_THE_YEAR",
                        "QUARTER_OF_THE_YEAR"
                      ]
                    },
                    "color": {
                      "description": "Line color theme",
                      "$ref": "#/$defs/_f7"
                    },
                    "axisNameDisplay": {
                      "description": "Which axis labels to show",
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "NONE",
                        "X",
                        "Y",
                        "BOTH"
                      ]
                    },
                    "displayDataLabel": {
                      "default": false,
                      "type": "boolean"
                    },
                    "displayLegend": {
                      "default": true,
                      "type": "boolean"
                    },
                    "isStacked": {
                      "description": "Stack multiple lines",
                      "type": "boolean"
                    },
                    "isCumulative": {
                      "description": "Show running totals",
                      "type": "boolean"
                    },
                    "rangeMin": {
                      "description": "Y axis minimum value",
                      "type": "number"
                    },
                    "rangeMax": {
                      "description": "Y axis maximum value",
                      "type": "number"
                    }
                  },
                  "required": [
                    "configurationType",
                    "aggregateFieldMetadataId",
                    "aggregateOperation",
                    "primaryAxisGroupByFieldMetadataId",
                    "displayDataLabel",
                    "displayLegend"
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "configurationType": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "const": "PIE_CHART"
                    },
                    "aggregateFieldMetadataId": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "format": "uuid"
                    },
                    "aggregateOperation": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "MIN",
                        "MAX",
                        "AVG",
                        "SUM",
                        "COUNT",
                        "COUNT_UNIQUE_VALUES",
                        "COUNT_EMPTY",
                        "COUNT_NOT_EMPTY",
                        "COUNT_TRUE",
                        "COUNT_FALSE",
                        "PERCENTAGE_EMPTY",
                        "PERCENTAGE_NOT_EMPTY"
                      ]
                    },
                    "groupByFieldMetadataId": {
                      "description": "Field UUID to slice by",
                      "type": "string",
                      "format": "uuid"
                    },
                    "groupBySubFieldName": {
                      "description": "REQUIRED for relation fields (e.g. \"name\", \"stage\") and composite fields (e.g. \"addressCity\"). Without this, relation fields group by raw UUID which is not useful.",
                      "type": "string"
                    },
                    "orderBy": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "FIELD_ASC",
                        "FIELD_DESC",
                        "FIELD_POSITION_ASC",
                        "FIELD_POSITION_DESC",
                        "VALUE_ASC",
                        "VALUE_DESC",
                        "MANUAL"
                      ]
                    },
                    "manualSortOrder": {
                      "type": "array",
                      "items": {
                        "type": "string"
                      }
                    },
                    "dateGranularity": {
                      "description": "Date grouping granularity when slicing by date",
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "DAY",
                        "WEEK",
                        "MONTH",
                        "QUARTER",
                        "YEAR",
                        "DAY_OF_THE_WEEK",
                        "MONTH_OF_THE_YEAR",
                        "QUARTER_OF_THE_YEAR"
                      ]
                    },
                    "color": {
                      "description": "Chart color theme",
                      "$ref": "#/$defs/_f7"
                    },
                    "displayDataLabel": {
                      "default": true,
                      "type": "boolean"
                    },
                    "displayLegend": {
                      "default": true,
                      "type": "boolean"
                    },
                    "showCenterMetric": {
                      "default": true,
                      "description": "Show aggregate value in center",
                      "type": "boolean"
                    },
                    "hideEmptyCategory": {
                      "default": false,
                      "description": "Hide slices with zero values",
                      "type": "boolean"
                    }
                  },
                  "required": [
                    "configurationType",
                    "aggregateFieldMetadataId",
                    "aggregateOperation",
                    "groupByFieldMetadataId",
                    "displayDataLabel",
                    "displayLegend",
                    "showCenterMetric",
                    "hideEmptyCategory"
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "configurationType": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "const": "IFRAME"
                    },
                    "url": {
                      "description": "URL to embed",
                      "type": "string",
                      "format": "uri"
                    }
                  },
                  "required": [
                    "configurationType"
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "configurationType": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "const": "STANDALONE_RICH_TEXT"
                    },
                    "body": {
                      "description": "Rich text content. Use { \"markdown\": \"your content here\" } for text. Supports full markdown syntax.",
                      "type": "object",
                      "properties": {
                        "blocknote": {
                          "description": "BlockNote JSON string (advanced). Stringified array of BlockNote blocks.",
                          "anyOf": [
                            {
                              "type": "string"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "null"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        "markdown": {
                          "description": "Markdown content string (preferred for AI). Supports headings, bold, lists, links, etc.",
                          "anyOf": [
                            {
                              "type": "string"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "null"
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  "required": [
                    "configurationType",
                    "body"
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "configurationType": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "const": "RECORD_TABLE"
                    },
                    "viewId": {
                      "description": "UUID of the dedicated view created for this widget. Must be created with create_view before creating the widget. Never reuse a record index view.",
                      "type": "string",
                      "format": "uuid"
                    }
                  },
                  "required": [
                    "configurationType",
                    "viewId"
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          },
          "required": [
            "title",
            "type",
            "gridPosition"
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    "required": [
      "title",
      "tabTitle",
      "widgets"
    ],
    "$defs": {
      "_f7": {
        "type": "string",
        "enum": [
          "auto",
          "red",
          "ruby",
          "crimson",
          "tomato",
          "orange",
          "amber",
          "yellow",
          "lime",
          "grass",
          "green",
          "jade",
          "mint",
          "turquoise",
          "cyan",
          "sky",
          "blue",
          "iris",
          "violet",
          "purple",
          "plum",
          "pink",
          "bronze",
          "gold",
          "brown",
          "gray"
        ]
      }
    }
  }
}